get

public final PolyPeptide get(Atom atom)
Returns the first PolyPeptide object that holds the atom. The search for the atom will be done based on reference and not by the .equal method.

Parameters:
atom - - Atom object to be searched in the PolyPeptide list members.
Returns:
PolyPeptide object holding the atom. If the atom could not be found in one of the PolyPeptide list members, than NULL is returned.
